<B>__{anna karenina}
<A>__{written by tom stoppard based on the novel by leo tolstoy.}
<L>__{interior pokrovskoe night}
<A>__{close expert fingers female, unlovely, capable shape a small lump of dough which, with some shreds of cabbage, becomes a filled bun called a pirozhok . . . which is now placed on a baking tray to join rows of pirozhoki ready for the oven. close one hand opens the oven, and, mittened by an apron, removes a tray of perfectly baked pirozhoki, which the other hand replaces with the fresh tray . . . slightly burning itself on a knuckle.}
